txt.en: 'Meow! Well, well, you are up to Book 6 of the Epic quest series. I wonder, are you getting tired of speaking to me yet? No? Well good! Because there so much left to the Epic quest after this book.\n\nBut that's for later. For now, if you want to complete Book 6 of the Epic quest, you'll be all set once you complete this quest.
'Well, you know how this works by now. Complete this quest and you'll have Book VI of the Epic quest completed.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book VI of the Epic quest series.
